which the manager is free to delete it).</p><p>The send option <code class="inline">extra</code> specifies an opaque data structure passed on to the
<code class="inline">net-if</code> process.
The <code class="inline">net-if</code> process included in this application makes, with one
exception, no use of this info, so the only use for it (when using the built in
<code class="inline">net-if</code>) would be tracing. The one usage exception is: <em>Any</em> tuple with
