          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">Result = ok | {error, Reason}</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Reason = <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:term/0">term</a>()</pre>

        </div>


<p>Changes the log size of the Audit Trail Log. The application must be configured
to use the audit trail log function. Please refer to disk_log(3) in Kernel
Reference Manual for a description of how to change the log size.</p><p>The change is permanent, as long as the log is not deleted. That means, the log
size is remembered across reboots.</p>
  </section>
</section>
