<section class="detail" id="format_reason/2">


    <span id="format_reason/1"></span>

  <div class="detail-header">
    <a href="#format_reason/2" class="detail-link" data-no-tooltip="" aria-label="Link to this function">
      <i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    </a>
    <div class="heading-with-actions">

        <div class="signature-row">
          <h1 class="signature" translate="no">format_reason(Reason)<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;≡&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result">format_reason/2</span></h1>


            <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/snmp/src/manager/snmpm.erl#L2172" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
              <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </a>

        </div>

      <div class="signature-row">




              <h1 class="signature" translate="no">format_reason(Prefix, Reason)<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result">FReason</span></h1>





          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/snmp/src/manager/snmpm.erl#L2193" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
            <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">


        <div class="specs">
          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">Prefix = <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:non_neg_integer/0">non_neg_integer</a>() | <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:string/0">string</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Reason = <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:term/0">term</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">FReason = <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:string/0">string</a>()</pre>

        </div>


<p>This utility function is used to create a formatted (pretty printable) string of
the error reason received from either:</p><ul><li>The <code class="inline">Reason</code> returned value if any of the sync/async get/get-next/set/get-bulk
functions returns <code class="inline">{error, Reason}</code></li><li>The <code class="inline">Reason</code> parameter in the <a href="snmpm_user.html#c:handle_error/3">handle_error</a> user
callback function.</li></ul><p><code class="inline">Prefix</code> should either be an indentation string (e.g. a list of spaces) or a
positive integer (which will be used to create the indentation string of that
length).</p>
  </section>
</section>
<section class="detail" id="info/0">


