            </a>

        </div>

      <div class="signature-row">




              <h1 class="signature" translate="no">sync_get_bulk2(UserId, TargetName, NonRep, MaxRep, Oids, SendOpts)<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result">Result</span></h1>




          <span class="note">(since OTP R14B03)</span>


