            <pre translate="no">Reason = <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:term/0">term</a>()</pre>

        </div>


<p>Unload a <code class="inline">Mib</code> from the manager. The <code class="inline">MibName</code> is the name of the Mib, including
the path to where the compiled mib is found. For example,</p><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="w">          </span><span class="n">Dir</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">code</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">priv_dir</span><span class="p" data-group-id="9311015826-1">(</span><span class="ss">my_app</span><span class="p" data-group-id="9311015826-1">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">++</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s">&quot;/mibs/&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
          </span><span class="nc">snmpm</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">unload_mib</span><span class="p" data-group-id="9311015826-2">(</span><span class="n">Dir</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">++</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s">&quot;MY-MIB&quot;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="9311015826-2">)</span><span class="p">.</span></code></pre>
  </section>
</section>
